cent military operation in Zamfara have infiltrated the state. September 23, 2016 In "News" …Nigeria shouldn’t be reduced to land of blood, tears, misery – NLC …Berates military hierarchy, insists on sacking of security chiefs …Gunmen strike again in Niger, kill 3 soldiers, Vigilante …Synergy between el-Rufa’i, CAN'll bring peace in Kaduna — Sen Uba Sani By Wole Mosadomi, Victor Ahiuma-Young, Johnbosco Agbakwuru &… August 19, 2020 In "News" Chadian military has continued to frown and condemn  their Nigerian counterparts for the policy of reintegrating repentant Boko Haram members. April 18, 2020 In "News"